CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

December 19, 2007

[Cite as 12/1912007 Case Announcements, 2007-Ohio-6770.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2006-1197. Disciplinary Counsel v. Johnson.

On application for reinstatement of Bryan Bright Johnson, Attorney Registration No. 0003981. Application granted, respondent reinstated to the practice of law in Ohio, and probation imposed.
